### Get all tasks
POST http://localhost:5000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { getAllTasks { id title description status } }"
}

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:5000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { createTask(title: \"Test Task\", description: \"A test task\", status: \"Pending\") { id title description status } }"
}

### Update a task's status
POST http://localhost:5000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { updateTaskStatus(id: \"<PUT_TASK_ID_HERE>\", status: \"Completed\") { id title description status } }"
}